Package com.telenav.kivakit.core.time

Class HourOfWeek

java.lang.Object
com.telenav.kivakit.core.time.BaseTime<HourOfWeek>
com.telenav.kivakit.core.time.HourOfWeek
All Implemented Interfaces:
Zeroable, AsString, StringFormattable, PointInTime<HourOfWeek,Duration>, TimeMeasurement, LongValued, Comparable<PointInTime<?,?>>
public class HourOfWeek extends BaseTime<HourOfWeek>
Represents an hour of the week, for example Thursday at 1pm. This class stores its count value in the fields dayOfWeek() and hourOfDay().
Author:
jonathanl (shibo)
